---
title: Chilli Glazed Salmon and Sticky Veg with Garlic Yoghurt Drizzle and Salad
description: Salmon is a delicate and flavoursome fish, perfect for absorbing flavours such as the spice blend and red pepper chilli jelly in this recipe. Paired with a refreshing cucumber salad and sticky roasted veg, it's a real catch!
